Package net.neto_framework.packets

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DisconnectPacket
    A disconnect packet can be sent to/from either server or client.
    EncryptionRequestPacket
    The encryption request packet is sent from server to client after the server has received a handshake.
    EncryptionResponsePacket
    The encryption response packet is sent client to server and contains the shared secret encrypted with the servers public key.
    HandshakePacket
    The handshake packet is the first packet send from client to server.
    NetoClientEventListener
    A client event listener used to listen to built-in packets.
    NetoServerEventListener
    A server event listener used to listen to built-in packets.
    SuccessPacket
    The success packet is sent from server to client and is the final packet involved in the handshake process.
